videos.headline: A'ja Wilson drops 35, leads Aces to Finals in OT
videos.description: A'ja Wilson's 35 points lead the Las Vegas Aces to an overtime victory against the Indiana Fever in Game 5 of the WNBA semifinals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Highlight (A'ja Wilson drops 35, leads Aces to Finals in OT) 2025/10/01 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Kelsey Mitchell knocks down a 3
videos.description: Kelsey Mitchell sinks a 3 to put the Fever in front 11-9.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Kelsey Mitchell knocks down a 3) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Megan Gustafson connects for the deep 3
videos.description: Megan Gustafson puts the Aces back on top 19-16 with a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Megan Gustafson connects for the deep 3) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shey Peddy knocks down the 3-pointer with ease
videos.description: Brianna Turner kicks it out to Shey Peddy for the deep 3 for the Fever in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Shey Peddy knocks down the 3-pointer with ease) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: NaLyssa Smith with a huge block
videos.description: NaLyssa Smith denies Aliyah Boston's layup at the rim early in the first quarter for the Aces.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (NaLyssa Smith with a huge block) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dana Evans sinks a 3 from behind the arc
videos.description: Dana Evans’ 3 pointer puts the Aces in front 26-25.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Dana Evans sinks a 3 from behind the arc) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Odyssey Sims cashes it from the top of the key
videos.description: The Fever share the ball and Odyssey Sims puts Indiana within 1.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Odyssey Sims cashes it from the top of the key) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Becky Hammon gets T'd up, has to be held back from refs
videos.description: Becky Hammon voices her displeasure at the referees and is issued a tech, having to be held back from the officials.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Becky Hammon gets T'd up, has to be held back from refs) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: A'ja Wilson's steal leads to a Jackie Young bucket for the Aces
videos.description: A’ja Wilson steals and finds Jackie Young, who finishes strong with a layup at the other end.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (A'ja Wilson's steal leads to a Jackie Young bucket for the Aces) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelsey Mitchell buries the 3
videos.description: Kelsey Mitchell at the top of the arc banks a 3-pointer to put the Fever within 4.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Kelsey Mitchell buries the 3) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackie Young knocks down the triple to stretch the Aces’ lead
videos.description: Jackie Young in rhythm sinks a 3-pointer to give the Aces a 64-55 lead.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Jackie Young knocks down the triple to stretch the Aces’ lead) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: A'ja Wilson drills it from deep
videos.description: A'ja Wilson gets the assist from Jackie Young to bury the 3-pointer for the Aces.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (A'ja Wilson drills it from deep) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kelsey Mitchell has to be helped off after injury
videos.description: During the third quarter, Kelsey Mitchell sustains an injury. A stretcher is brought out, but she's able to walk off with assistance.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Kelsey Mitchell has to be helped off after injury) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shey Peddy lets a trey fly to close the gap for the Fever
videos.description: Shey Peddy sinks a 3-pointer in the fourth to bring the Fever within five points.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Shey Peddy lets a trey fly to close the gap for the Fever) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: A'ja Wilson boosts Aces' lead in 4th quarter
videos.description: A'ja Wilson drives and finishes with a score to give the Aces a 77-68 lead in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (A'ja Wilson boosts Aces' lead in 4th quarter) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Odyssey Sims, Aliyah Boston keep it close for Fever
videos.description: Odyssey Sims and Aliyah Boston score late in the fourth to keep the Fever close to the Aces.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Odyssey Sims, Aliyah Boston keep it close for Fever) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Odyssey Sims ties it for Fever late in 4th
videos.description: A'ja Wilson can't come up with a steal, and Odyssey Sims is able to drive and tie the score at 86 late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Odyssey Sims ties it for Fever late in 4th) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jewell Loyd drains corner 3 for Las Vegas in OT
videos.description: Jewell Loyd gets the ball in the corner and cashes in on a 3-pointer for the Aces in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Jewell Loyd drains corner 3 for Las Vegas in OT) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chelsea Gray buries a clutch trey for Aces in OT
videos.description: Chelsea Gray's 3-pointer gives the Aces a four-point lead over the Fever in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Chelsea Gray buries a clutch trey for Aces in OT) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Game 5 goes to OT after Aces can't convert game-winning attempt
videos.description: The Aces try to score the game-winning bucket, but they are unsuccessful in the final seconds of regulation, sending Game 5 vs. the Fever to overtime.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Game 5 goes to OT after Aces can't convert game-winning attempt) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chelsea Gray continues her takeover in OT
videos.description: Chelsea Gray scores to give the Aces a six-point lead over the Fever in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Chelsea Gray continues her takeover in OT) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shey Peddy comes up big for Indiana with a triple in OT
videos.description: Shey Peddy lands a triple that makes it a one-possession game for the Fever late in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Shey Peddy comes up big for Indiana with a triple in OT) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aces celebrate 3rd trip to WNBA Finals in 4 years
videos.description: The Las Vegas Aces celebrate after defeating the Fever in OT of Game 5 to return to the WNBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Aces celebrate 3rd trip to WNBA Finals in 4 years) 2025/10/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: A'ja Wilson, Jackie Young lead Aces back to Finals with combined 67 points
videos.description: A'Ja Wilson and Jackie Young combine to score 67 points as the Aces outlast the Fever in overtime to book a trip to the WNBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Highlight (A'ja Wilson, Jackie Young lead Aces back to Finals with combined 67 points) 2025/10/01 ESHEET
